info.urushi.roof_225: Place this on any kind of Slabs.

info.urushi.ricecauldron: Place Dirt Furnace below and put Raw Rice in it.

info.urushi.rawrice: Use Rice Ears to Senbakoki to get 2x Raw Rice.

info.urushi.placeablefood: Click with sneaking to place this food.

info.urushi.under_development: Now under development. Wait for the future update!
info.urushi.shichirin1: Ignite, put fuels into, and right-click with Uchiwa!
info.urushi.shichirin2: For the first 5 seconds, the intensity of the fire does not affect the cooking result.
info.urushi.shichirin3: Make the duration of ☆ and the duration of ★ as equal as possible!
info.urushi.magatama1: Right-click on Onusa to send Reiryoku into Magatama.
info.urushi.magatama2: Many items will be available while this is in your inventory.
info.urushi.sanbo: Items can be crafted in conjunction with a Birch Altar.
info.urushi.sacred_rock2: When you place a block of specific element in front of this, the block will be absorbed and generate Reiryoku.
info.urushi.sacred_rock3: The face which has long paper is front.
info.urushi.emitter1: You can extract Reiryoku with this.
info.urushi.emitter2: Send a Redstone signal to be idle.
info.urushi.emitter3: Curve the Reiryoku signals with a Mirror.
info.urushi.emitter4: Place a Onusa at crossing points.
info.urushi.tank2: Place this at crossing points of Reiryoku transmitting.
info.urushi.mirror1: You can curve Reiryoku signals with this.
info.urushi.mirror2: You can also curve signals diagonally.
info.urushi.mirror4: Due to under development, you cannot transmit Reiryoku for up or down directions.
info.urushi.element_crafting_table1: By placing Birch Sanbos around this, you can craft many items.
info.urushi.element_crafting_table2: You need send specific Reiryoku into this.
info.urushi.amber_igniter1: Consume 10 fire element Reiryoku to ignite a Shichirin.
info.urushi.uchiwa2: Consume 10 wood element Reiryoku to manipulate the fire of Shichirin.
info.urushi.uchiwa3: Consume 1 wood element Reiryoku per one block.
info.urushi.kitsunebi3: Consume 100 fire element Reiryoku to place or toss this.
info.urushi.wagasa2: Consume wood element Reiryoku to use.
